  "translations": {
    "en": "And do takbir after Maghrib, the final Isha, the morning prayer, and the Eid prayer, just as you do takbir in the days of Tashriq, saying: \"God is the Greatest, God is the Greatest, there is no god but God, and God is the Greatest, God is the Greatest, and to God belongs all praise, God is the Greatest for what He has guided us to, and praise be to God for what He has made us face.\"",
    "ur": "اور مغرب، عشاء آخرہ، صبح کی نماز اور عید کی نماز کے بعد تکبیر کہو۔",
    "tr": "Akşam, yatsı, sabah ve bayram namazından sonra Teşrik günlerinde tekbir getirdiğin gibi tekbir getir.",
    "fa": "و بعد از مغرب، عشاء آخر، نماز صبح و نماز عید تکبیر بگو.",
    "id": "Dan bertakbirlah setelah Maghrib, Isya akhir, shalat Subuh dan shalat Ied.",
    "bn": "এবং মাগরিব, শেষ ইশা, ফজর নামাজ ও ঈদের নামাজের পর তাকবীর বলো।",
    "es": "Y haz takbir después del Maghrib, la última Isha, la oración de la mañana y la oración del Eid.",
    "fr": "Et fais le takbir après le Maghrib, la dernière Isha, la prière du matin et la prière de l'Aïd.",
    "de": "Und sprich Takbir nach dem Maghrib, dem letzten Isha, dem Morgengebet und dem Eid-Gebet.",
    "ru": "И произноси такбир после магриба, последнего иша, утренней и праздничной молитвы.",
    "zh": "并在昏礼、末宵礼、晨礼和节日礼拜后念大赞词。"
  }
}